{"tid":1716888,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"林鄭以為不割蓆只係口號，唔知和理非同勇武早已建立無法斷裂嘅情感聯繫","createTime":"2019-11-13T12:51:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-13T16:20:03.000Z","uid":275829,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"5440e0a73e9ff1c1344527509eefd323691d5f84","tid":1716888,"uid":275829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T12:51:47.000Z","msg":"呢場革命，點解去到咁耐？靠嘅係所有手足團結一致，合作無間<br />\n林鄭錯判形勢，不懂人性<br />\n以為每日強烈讉責，指責示威者堵路破壞燒狗屋就可以離間勇和，令到和理非嬲自己人，阻自己返學返工<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">傻啦，無可能架</span></span><br />\n<br />\n我話你聽，作為一個和理非<br />\n當你唔再只係識得講等天收、落地獄，係FB/IG到打好嬲好嬲瞓唔着再配張灰色圖，而係<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">企前啲，再企前啲</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">- 積極籌組工會，以罷工為一大目標<br />\n- 整文宣，貼文宣，爭取最短時間要所有手足知道抗爭日程<br />\n- 罷買藍店，幫襯黃店，令到中資仆街，建立黃色經濟圈養活自己人<br />\n- 捐錢，籌旗，熟讀所有防具組合型號、魔法材料，無間段運送物資俾前線手足<br />\n- 做哨，義載，開放商鋪屋企俾佢哋暫避，盡量保障手足性命安全<br />\n- 一要人就落樓，萬人響應，幫手做盾，增加士氣</span></span><br />\n<br />\n就算你永遠都唔知佢哋嘅真名，永遠冇見過佢哋真容，永遠冇佢哋嘅電話<br />\n但當你真正同過佢哋傾一次計<br />\n真正痛佢哋所痛，憂佢哋所憂<br />\n當你真正視同行兒女為手足為家人<br />\n<br />\n你係永遠都唔會同屋企人割蓆架！！！！！<br />\n<br />\n林鄭嘅愚昧在於佢唔明白我哋所有人都不斷學習緊，逼自己企前再企前，就算做唔到矛都努力唔拖後退，支援戰士。佢理解唔到我哋何以一呼百應，圍魏救趙。佢冇朋友，冇手足，唔知咩叫團結友愛，萬眾一心。終其一生佢都唔會明白自己一手搞嘅送中，點解會令真香港人從心聯結，無法割裂。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">願榮光歸香港</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ae50db7eed3761534e9d05c20e33471627eda82","tid":1716888,"uid":43939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T12:56:04.000Z","msg":"番唔到轉頭嫁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"349763812baf14be4af12a963abfd5c15d1091a9","tid":1716888,"uid":194560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T13:00:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6be40afb1161ef1e201440e30b5b461fc320cc40","tid":1716888,"uid":275829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T13:13:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a80c435c4e15c3bf07604c719d7fc43b6552832","tid":1716888,"uid":275829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T14:03:19.000Z","msg":"罷啦罷罷罷<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"410746079db4cbe9c4a51251efae7d7741237bef","tid":1716888,"uid":275829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T15:00:00.000Z","msg":"自推1"},{"pid":"9a01cdc1b1674eb1ff853da5986f7b69d8c00e3f","tid":1716888,"uid":275829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T16:20:03.000Z","msg":"自推2"}]}